# February Roadmap 

## Goal
Build a daily habit, solve challenges, and write notes.

## Weekly Plan

**Week 1 (Feb 1–7)**
- Practice every day, even if only a little
- Solve easy challenges (aim for 5–10)
- Write your first note about one challenge

**Week 2 (Feb 8–14)**
- Try some medium challenges
- Think about what types of challenges you like best
- Write a short weekly summary

**Week 3 (Feb 15–21)**
- Try harder challenges if you can
- Practice solving challenges with a time limit
- Write notes about what you learned

**Week 4 (Feb 22–28)**
- Do a mini practice contest (CTF) or review your past work
- Write a weekly summary
- Prepare your monthly report

## Monthly Goals
- Practice every day
- Solve 5 to 10 challenges each week
- Write at least 3 notes or summaries
- Learn 2 new tools or techniques
- Keep a habit going for at least 14 days straight
